name: Spore Finance
description: Spore Finance is an ecosystem of algorithmically generated NFTs and a prediction market fueled by SPORE, a reflection token born in the Avalanche network. A bridge between the Avalanche C-chain and the BSC allows transferring SPORE while preserving the same supply. On the Avalanche side, 3% of every transaction is reflected and 3% is burned; on BSC, the whole 6% is burned. Buy $SPORE on Pancakeswap and transfer it to the Avalanche network to enjoy the SPORE reflection and let your Spores grow!
